                     Buckets: 4096  Batches: 2  Memory Usage: 47kB
                    ->  Seq Scan on customer c  (cost=0.00..14.99 rows=599 width=10) (actual time=0.008..0.077 rows=599 loops=1)
        ->  Hash  (cost=75.81..75.81 rows=4581 width=8) (actual time=1.950..1.950 rows=4581 loops=1)
